quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  77,41,righteous vol gxu shade printemp
  77,42,Kaj frukt ti ili dezir
  77,43,Mangx trink happily dors your works
  77,44,Ni tiel rekompenc des virtuous
  77,45,Ve ke tag al rejectors
  77,46,Mangx gxu temporarily; vi est kulp
  77,47,Ve ke tag al rejectors
  77,48,When ili told Bow down ili ne bow down
  77,49,Ve ke tag al rejectors
  77,50,Which Hadith this ili uphold